title: Vehicle Capacity Profile V5

vehicle_capacity_profile_id.title: Vehicle Capacity Profile ID
vehicle_capacity_profile_id.description: A unique internal identification of the vehicle capacity profile.

max_revenue.title: Maximum Revenue

deleted_at.title: Deleted At
deleted_at.description: When the vehicle capacity profile was deleted

created_at.title: Created At
created_at.description: When the vehicle capacity profile was created.

updated_at.title: Upated At
updated_at.description: When the vehicle capacity profile was updated.

max_volume_unit.title: Maximum Volume Unit
max_volume_unit.description: The units in which the maximum volume of the vehicle capacity profile is measured (cu ft, cu m).

max_weight_unit.title: Maximum Weight Unit
max_weight_unit.description: The units in which the maximum weight of the vehicle capacity profile is measured (kg, lb).
